Interface DocumentRoot

All Superinterfaces:

DocumentRootImpl
public interface DocumentRoot
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Document Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Db Connection
  • Meta Data Column
  • Meta Data Table
